FROM trans t
JOIN account a ON t.account_id = a.account_id
JOIN client c ON a.district_id = c.district_id

493:
SELECT 
    (COUNT(*) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM client c JOIN district d ON c.district_id = d.district_id WHERE d.A11 > 10000 AND c.gender = 'F')) * 100 AS percentage
FROM 
    client c JOIN district d ON c.district_id = d.district_id
WHERE 
    c.district_id IN (SELECT district_id FROM district WHERE A11 > 10000) AND c.gender = 'F';	----- bird -----	financial

SELECT (SUM(CASE WHEN loan.date = '1997-01-01' THEN loan.amount ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN loan.date = '1996-01-01' THEN loan.amount ELSE 0 END)) / SUM(CASE WHEN loan.date = '1996-01-01' THEN loan.amount ELSE 0 END) * 100 AS growth_rate
FROM loan
JOIN client ON loan.account_id = client.client_id
WHERE client.gender = 'M';	----- bird -----	financial

       (strftime('%Y', 'now') - strftime('%Y', c.birth_date)) AS age
FROM client c
